# ============================================================================
# iHymns — Example .htpasswd file
#
# DO NOT use this file directly. Generate a real .htpasswd file using:
#
#   htpasswd -c /home/<username>/.htpasswd-ihymns admin
#
# Store the real file OUTSIDE the web root (e.g., in your home directory).
# Update the AuthUserFile path in private_html/.htaccess to match.
#
# Format: username:encrypted_password
# ============================================================================

# Example entry (NOT a real password — do not use):
# admin:$apr1$xyz12345$ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPqrstuv0
